<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1057.66434.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Holotype of Multistria orthotropa gen. et sp. nov. A habitus in dorsal view B head and thorax in dorsal view C hind tarsus D pronotum in dorsal view. Scale bars: 2 mm (A); 1 mm (B, C); 0.25 mm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/580847" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1057.66434.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Line drawings of Multistria orthotropa gen. et sp. nov. A head and thorax B hind tarsus C forewing D hind wing. Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B); 2 mm (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/580848" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

